ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisAppointment of CURDIS KARREL of Sydney, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, or until the dissolution of the Cape Breton Growth Fund Corporation, whichever occurs first.
